background_description: The scene features a steep, dark green forested hill on the left, a concrete and stone seawall along the coast, and a dark, wet, muddy beach in the foreground. The calm water of the sea stretches into the distance, with several small boats anchored. Hazy blue-grey mountains line the far horizon, under a bright blue sky with scattered white clouds.
